query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('browser',
'centos',
'client',
'coding-style',
'cors',
'cuda',
'd3.js',
'g++',
'google-analytics',
'google-api',
'newline',
'oracle10g',
'user-interface',
'youtube-api');
